data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET DUE TO FINANCING. Great starter home! Corner lot. Large, fenced in backyard. High Ceilings. Centrally located between bases for easy access. Roof is only 5 years old; hot water heater installed 2023; a/c motor replaced in 2022. Nest thermostat and Vivent security system remain. Solar panels have alleviated electric bill, sans the basic FPL fee for service!!!Owners started a remodel but ran out of funds. The hard part has been done (removing carpet); ready for you to put your own touch!
